  <title>Load a file</title>

  <p>You can open a file, or many, by pressing the <gui>Add</gui> button on the upper left
  of the window. Select the files you want to shred, and click OK.
  </p>

  <p>You can also drag and drop the files you want to shred all at once into an
  open <app>File Shredder</app> window.</p>

   <note style="info">
    <p>The shredding button is hidden while there are no files loaded, and
    during shredding.</p>
  </note>

